dc_title_s: M.M. Dickson & Co.'s township and sectional pocket map of Washtenaw County, Michigan.; Township and sectional pocket map of Washtenaw County, Michigan.
dc_description_s: Cadastral map showing land ownership. Cover title. Includes index by township. 1 map: col.; 60 x 78 cm. folded in cover 17 x 11 cm.  booklet (35 p.; 17 cm.) This map is in the public domain. Please attribute access and use of this digitized map to the Stephen S. Clark Library, University of Michigan Library.
